WEBVTT

00:03:58.411 --> 00:04:00.115
Bu shunchaki omad edi.

00:04:00.115 --> 00:04:02.355
Agar Ebola ko'plab shaharlar
hududlariga yetib

00:04:02.355 --> 00:04:05.877
borganida, kasallanganlarning soni
judayam yuqori bo'lar edi.

00:04:05.877 --> 00:04:09.466
Keyingi bor bizga omad kulib
boqmasligi mumkin.

00:04:09.466 --> 00:04:14.530
Keyingi virus shunday bo'lishi mumkinki,
kasallanganlarda samolyot orqali sayohat

00:04:14.530 --> 00:04:17.842
qilishga yoki bozorlarga borishga
kuch bo'lishi mumkin. Virus Ebolaga

00:04:17.842 --> 00:04:20.846
o'xshash tabiatga ega bo'lishi 
ham mumkin, yoki bioterroristlar

00:04:20.846 --> 00:04:22.826
tomonidan yaratilishi mumkin.

00:04:22.826 --> 00:04:27.474
Demak, vaziyatni ming marta xavfliroq 
tus oldirishi mumkin bo'lgan narsalar bor.

00:04:27.474 --> 00:04:33.475
Keling, virusning havo orqali yuqishi
mumkin bo'lgan modelini ko'rib chiqaylik.